sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Cliente
  participant G as Gateway 3s
  participant P as servico-pix 2.5s
  participant L as servico-limites 1.5s
  C->>G: POST /pix
  G->>P: deadline restante
  P->>L: timeout interno menor
  Note over G,L: Timeout externo maior que interno
  L-->>P: resposta ou timeout
  P-->>G: resposta
  G-->>C: 200 ou 504
